      "content": "everything's gone. the firm, the funding, everything. i looked at the bank statements today and i don't even recognize myself anymore. i just feel like a ghost walking around in a suit. i can't even think about going back home... the look on my parents' faces, the way people in the industry will look at me... i just don't see a version of the future where i'm not this failure. it's too much to carry.",
