      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel trapped when the weight of debt and shame feels unbearable, but the idea that you have to \"fix\" yourself is just another way to let the pain dictate your path. Sometimes the only way to stop the crushing is to let go of the need to be perfect or to earn forgiveness from those who hurt you. You deserve to be free of this suffocating feeling, and that freedom begins when you stop carrying the burden of their judgments.",
